flowchart LR
  contributor[Contributor or agent]
  reviewer[Reviewer or maintainer]
  github[Git and PR review]
  adapters[Codex, Claude Code, and opencode users]

  subgraph repo_boundary[RigorLoop repository boundary]
    repo[RigorLoop repository system]
    validation[Repository-owned validation scripts]
    generated[Generated runtime and adapter packages]
  end

  contributor -->|authors specs, architecture, ADRs, templates, skills, and plans| repo
  reviewer -->|reviews diffs, C4 views, arc42 sections, ADRs, and evidence| repo
  github -->|runs repository-owned checks and carries review history| validation
  repo -->|selects and executes validation| validation
  repo -->|generates synchronized guidance| generated
  generated -->|published or copied adapter guidance| adapters
